      <div class="msgContentFrame">Feature REquest: Quivers for Arrows. <br /> <br />Please implement quivers that turn into 99 arrows even if they only stack to 12 it will help so much at attracting and retaining players.  Every archer i know is on the verge of quitting the game because they cant craft or farm because their inventory is completely full of arrows.  Because the arrows are used up so fast they cant ever make any money or stay on top of being able to afford arrows.<div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div><img src="http://common.zam.com/xivsigs/290155.png" alt="Signature Image" border="0" /> <br /> <br />Cornyboob Funnyname Wutai  Phys 47 Conj 33 Weave 35 LW 25 Alch 23 Glad 18 Thaum 17 Pug 13 GS 8 Bot 9 Miner 8 Shield 19 Maur 3 <br /></div></div>
